g.text: As a user, I can view a list of all articles
As a user, I can view an individual article
As a user, I can view comments for an article
As a user, I can vote on an article
As a user, I can post a new comment to an existing article
As a user, I can delete only my own comments
As a user, I can view a separate page of articles on each topic
As a user, I can sort articles by date, comment count, or votes
As a user, when I go to a missing page I get a helpful error
